These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
Food: eggplant, pear, cauliflower, garlic
1. Food:eggplant is on the far left##1
2. Food:pear is on the left or right of Food:eggplant##3
3. Food:pear is on the left or right of Food:cauliflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | eggplant | pear | cauliflower | garlic |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
Beverage: cola, milk, mirinda, lemonade
1. Beverage:cola is on the right of Beverage:milk##1
2. Beverage:lemonade is on the left of Beverage:mirinda##1
3. Beverage:mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | cola | lemonade | mirinda |

 #################################
 
